snippet.title: Forager - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
In Forager, a 2D open world game, start small and improve your base, skills, equipment, network of friends – and enemies! – and build your future as you see fit! You can seek out Forager soon on Nintendo Switch.

#NintendoSwitch #Forager
